  "detailed_description": "Recursive pain is a fast-paced third person multiplayer shooter that brings many original ideas and gameplay mechanics to the online-shooters genre.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Novelty comes first – original gameplay mechanics</h2><br>The main purpose of the project is to constantly develop, continuously search, test and introduce new gameplay mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/384d9d1159ac34c7c402395a4a84d096.poster.avif?t=1706704252\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/384d9d1159ac34c7c402395a4a84d096.webm?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/384d9d1159ac34c7c402395a4a84d096.mp4?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BLINDSIGHT </strong>- Navigate in complete darkness using echolocation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/579de62d4f630913f150b263daddb60a.poster.avif?t=1706704252\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/579de62d4f630913f150b263daddb60a.webm?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/579de62d4f630913f150b263daddb60a.mp4?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DILEMMA </strong>- Altered gravity. The players can run on any surfaces, as well as use the teleportation. Be careful because enemies can be anywhere. Nevertheless, you can be anywhere as well.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/d4da443c85ca132a19c0c03ef96b1cd9.poster.avif?t=1706704252\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/d4da443c85ca132a19c0c03ef96b1cd9.webm?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/d4da443c85ca132a19c0c03ef96b1cd9.mp4?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BLANK </strong>- Shoot paintballs in order to paint any objects and enemies. Do not stay in the painted areas or you will be quickly noticed <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/e850ada1fb1f8e74ef1a50d6b9703218.poster.avif?t=1706704252\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/e850ada1fb1f8e74ef1a50d6b9703218.webm?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/e850ada1fb1f8e74ef1a50d6b9703218.mp4?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>ADVAITA </strong>- on this map player can see only a small area of reality.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/18dfeedc6566dfbd8b70e6948b1eb544.poster.avif?t=1706704252\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/18dfeedc6566dfbd8b70e6948b1eb544.webm?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/968360/extras/18dfeedc6566dfbd8b70e6948b1eb544.mp4?t=1706704252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>POISON </strong>- The snow is poisonous, so it causes damage to players. Shoot paintballs to pave your way.  Move only on the painted areas in order not to cause damage to yourself.<br><br><strong>And this is just the beginning!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME MODES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deathmatch<br></li><li>Team Deathmatch<br></li><li>Capture The Flag <br></li><li>Hardcore – The goal is to be the last live player. The last alive player wins the round. Player who has survived in more rounds wins the match. <br></li><li>Team Hardcore<br></li><li>Raid – each team has a flag that must be protected. The goal is to capture the enemy flag and take it to the team base, or eliminate the enemy team.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Players can host dedicated servers.<br></li><li>Skills.<br></li><li>Online multiplayer, with either dedicated or listen (player hosted) servers. <br></li><li>Flexible game settings – min and max players, auto-team balance, allowed skills, etc…<br></li><li>LAN support.</li></ul><br>Join our Discord to talk with the devs or to organize matches - ",
